import Button from "./Button"
import Input from "./Input"

function Form() {
  return (
   <form className="flex flex-col " action="#" >
    {/* <label for="inputName" className="flex flex-col text-[14px] text-denim font-sans font-normal mb-[24px]"> Name
      <input type="text" id="inputName" name="inputName" placeholder="e.g. Stephen King"/>
    </label>
    <label for="inputMail" className="flex flex-col text-[14px] text-denim font-sans font-normal mb-[24px]"> Email Address
      <input type="email" id="inputMail" name="inputMail" placeholder="e.g. stephenking@lorem.com"/>
    </label>
    <label for="inputPhone" className="flex flex-col text-[14px] text-denim font-sans font-normal mb-[24px]"> Phone Number
      <input type="tel" id="inputPhone" name="inputPhone" placeholder="e.g. +1 234 567 890"/>
    </label> */}
    <Input for="inputName" type="text" placeholder="e.g. Stephen King"/>
    <Input for="inputMail" type="email" placeholder="e.g. stephenking@lorem.com"/>
    <Input for="inputPhone" type="tel" placeholder="e.g. +1 234 567 890"/>
    <Button />
   </form>
  )
}

export default Form
